quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  48,1,"Min ngudditanii ma uddital …ďanngungal,"
  48,2,"fii no Allah yaafoma ko ngardin…óaa e bakkaat, e ko sakkitii, e fii no O timminira neema makko on e maa…óa, O feewne e laawol po'occiingol."
  48,3,"e no Allah wallirma ballal tii…óngal."
  48,4,"Ko KaŇčko woni jippin…óo dee∆īere nden e …ďer…óe gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen, fii no …ďe …ďeydora gooŇč…óinal e dow gooŇč…óinal ma…ď…ďe ngal. Ko Allah woodani koneeji kammuuji …óiin e leydi ndin; Allah siforii won'de ganndu…óo, √Ďee√Ī…óo,"
  48,5,"e fii no O naadira gooŇč…óin…ďe wor…ďe …ďen e gooŇč…óin…ďe rew…ďe …ďen, Aljannaaji …ói can…ói ilata ley mum, ko …ď…óe duumotoo…ďe e majji, e no O montira-na…ďe ban…ói ma…ď…ďe …óin. ∆äuum wonii ka Allah, malal mawnungal."
  48,6,"E no O leptira naafiqii…ďe wor…ďe …ďeen e naafiqii…ďe rew…ďe …ďeen, e sirkoo…ďe wor…ďe …ďen e sirkoo…ďe rew…ďe …ďen, sikkoo…ďe Allah sikke bon…óe. Yiiloonde bon…ói ngonii e dow ma…ď…ďe. Allah tikkanii…ďe kadi, O hu…óii …ďe, O hebilanii …ďe Jahannama. Nge bonii ruttorde !"
  48,7,"Ko Allah woodani konuuji kammuuli …óiin e leydi ndin. Allah siforii won'de 'ool…óo, √Ďee√Ī…óo."
  48,8,"Min nulirii ma seedotoo…óo, wewlinoowo, e jeertinoowo,"
  48,9,"fii no gooŇč…óiniron Allah e Nulaa…óo makko on, mawninon mo, teddinon mo, subbunhinano…óon mo bimmbi e kiikii…óe."